        "id": "SR_BAROLO_1.2",
        "text": "The app dashboard shall display the current overall status of the currently selected appliance according to the product-defined appliance status model, including distinguishable normal/available and attention-or-issue states where applicable; if the status cannot be determined, the dashboard shall display a clear unknown or unavailable status and shall not display a misleading normal status.",
        "happyFlow": "Given a user with access opens the dashboard for a selected appliance, when the app obtains the appliance's overall status, then the dashboard displays the status for that selected appliance using the product-defined status model.",
