        "id": "SR_BAROLO_2.1",
        "text": "The app dashboard shall display, for each temperature-controlled zone of the currently selected accessible wine appliance, the latest available measured zone temperature with a clear zone association and temperature unit according to the applicable user or product temperature-unit setting; if a measured temperature for a zone cannot be determined, the dashboard shall display an unavailable indication for that specific zone.",
        "happyFlow": "Given a user with access opens the dashboard for a wine appliance with one or more temperature-controlled zones, when measured temperatures are available, then the dashboard displays one measured temperature per zone, each with the correct zone association and unit of measure.",
