          "Given the target temperature differs from the measured temperature, when the dashboard displays zone temperature, then the displayed value is the measured temperature and not the target temperature."
        ],
        "exceptionFlows": [
          "Given the measured temperature for one zone cannot be determined, when the dashboard is displayed, then only that zone shows temperature unavailable while other zones with known measured temperatures continue to display their values.",
